### 7. Trọng tài Submit Kết Quả trận đấu
POST {{baseUrl}}/referee/matches/{{rankedBookingId}}/result
Authorization: Bearer {{refereeToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refereeUserId": {{refereeId}},
  "teamAScore": 11,
  "teamBScore": 8,
  "winningTeam": "A"
}

### 8. Player 1 Confirm Kết quả
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{rankedBookingId}}/confirm-result
Authorization: Bearer {{player1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerUserId": {{player1Id}},
  "accepted": true
}

